text: Eugene Ronald Hiscock (born June 27, 1950) was a Canadian politician. He represented the electoral district of Eagle River in the Newfoundland and Labrador House of Assembly from 1979 to 1989. He was a member of the Liberal Party.Encyclopedia of Newfoundland and Labrador He was born at Chamberlains, Newfoundland. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Liberal Party of Newfoundland and Labrador MHAs Category:People from Conception Bay South
